01.10 COMMENT FIXED RATE LOAN AMORTIZATION SCHEDULE
01.20 COMMENT INPUT PRINCIPAL ANNUAL RATE AND MONTHS
01.30 ASK P
01.40 ASK A
01.50 ASK N
01.60 SET R=A/1200
01.70 SET X=(1+R)^N
01.80 SET M=P*R*X/(X-1)
01.90 SET B=P
02.10 SET T=0
02.20 SET Q=0
02.30 COMMENT PAYMENT THEN MONTHLY BALANCE TABLE
02.40 PRINT M,!
02.50 FOR I=1,N; DO 3
02.60 SET O=M*N
02.70 SET C=O-P
02.80 COMMENT TOTAL PAID AND TOTAL INTEREST
02.90 PRINT O,!,C
02.95 EXIT
03.10 SET J=B*R
03.20 SET K=M-J
03.30 SET B=B-K
03.40 SET T=T+J
03.50 SET Q=Q+K
03.60 PRINT I,J,K,B,!
03.70 RETURN
04.10 COMMENT TABLE COLUMNS MONTH INTEREST PRINCIPAL BALANCE
04.20 COMMENT RATE IS ENTERED AS ANNUAL PERCENT
04.30 COMMENT PAYMENT IS CONSTANT EXCEPT FINAL ROUNDING
04.40 COMMENT EARLY PAYMENTS CONTAIN MORE INTEREST
04.50 COMMENT LATE PAYMENTS CONTAIN MORE PRINCIPAL
04.60 COMMENT TOTAL INTEREST IS ACCUMULATED IN T
04.70 COMMENT TOTAL PRINCIPAL IS ACCUMULATED IN Q
04.80 COMMENT ZERO RATE REQUIRES PRINCIPAL DIVIDED BY MONTHS
04.90 COMMENT VALUES USE THE ACTIVE MK61 NUMBER FORMAT
